saytime-weather (1.1.5) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Simplified command line arguments in saytime.pl:
    - Now only accepts zipcode, node, silent, and 24hour options
    - Removed hour and minute arguments
    - Added better argument validation and usage messages
  * Fixed argument handling to use current time only
  * Improved error messages for invalid arguments
  * Enhanced documentation for command line usage

 -- Jory A. Pratt <geekypenguin@gmail.com>  Wed, 20 Mar 2024 12:00:00 -0500

